          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a small pot with 10g <span class=\"text-danger\">[20g]</span> <strong>butter</strong> over a low heat</p><p>Once melted, remove the pot from the heat and add the <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Stir everything together until fully combined with a sauce-like consistency – this is your<strong> buffalo sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
